title: Amazing 3 Bed 1 Bath Duplex
posting_body: ['576 Bay Street Saint Paul, Minnesota 55105', 'Price: $1595.00', 'Deposit: $1595.00', 'Amazing W 7th location!', 'Large 3 bed, 1 bath side x side duplex w/front and rear private entrances.', ' Property features plank flooring on the main floor, hardwood floors upstairs, original woodwork and so much more.', 'Upon entering you’ll notice a main floor bedroom plus the spacious living and dining area that leads into the kitchen.', ' Kitchen leads to the back porch with large deck.', '2 beds and full bath located on the upper level.', 'W/D in basement.', 'Unit comes with 1 off-street parking spot.', 'Tenant pays gas and electric only!', 'Snow/lawn, water/sewer and trash included in rent.', 'Available now – 1 yr lease term.', 'No cats.', '2 dogs max under 100lbs w/$150 per month pet rent per pet.', ' Every pet/animal must go through professional screening process and apply.', 'The fee is $20 for the 1st pet and $15 for each additional, if applicable paid directly to the 3rd party screening vendor.', '$20/pet app fee paid at time of move in.', 'Application Fee: $45/ adult non-refundable.', 'Information deemed reliable but not guaranteed.', 'Renters insurance required.', 'Section 8 not approved.', 'No cats.', '2 dogs max under 100lbs w/$150 per month pet rent per pet.', ' Every pet/animal must go through professional screening process and apply.', 'The fee is $20 for the 1st pet and $15 for each additional, if applicable paid directly to the 3rd party screening vendor.', '$20/pet app fee paid at time of move in.', 'Property Features', 'Duplex', '3 bed', '1 bath', 'deck', 'Hardwood Floors', 'Off-Street Parking', 'Porch', 'Visit our website at <URL> for more information.']
